# Temporary ignore — large recently-generated assets that bloat deploys.
# Remove specific entries here when those assets need to go live.
# This unblocks small content updates (lyrics, hub pages) when full upload times out.

# Heavy generated manga PNGs (1200x11000px / 11-17MB each) — original scrolls.
# Compressed JPGs in /manga/web/ are deployed instead; manga.html reader points there.
manga/kompis_s*.png
manga/rougeina_s*.png
manga/smurjan_s*.png
manga/trollmage_s*.png
manga/vigolas_s*.png
manga/chapter_*.png
manga/enhanced/

# Wan21 enhanced clips (290MB)
clips_assets/enhanced/

# Episode MP4s already on /su-vault-9x7k/origins (newer ones can be ignored too)
episodes/bakasura/
episodes/kali/

# Local dev / cache
.vercel/
node_modules/
*.log

# ===== SECURITY — NEVER DEPLOY SECRETS (belt-and-suspenders) =====
# .env lives ABOVE this deploy root so it's already out of scope, but block it
# here too in case the tree layout ever changes. Same for any credential file.
.env
.env.*
*.env
*token*.json
*secret*.json
*credential*.json
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.bak
tools/youtube_creds/
**/youtube_creds/
